text: The iPhone 5 is a smartphone made by Apple. It is the sixth generation of the iPhone, the next smartphone after the iPhone 4S and before the iPhone 5S and iPhone 5C. It was revealed on September 12, 2012 and then released on September 21, 2012. ==References== ==Other websites== * 5 Category:Mobile phones introduced in 2012 Category:Apple products released in 2012
